# NETWORK::CLOUD_DELETE_MEMBER_FILE

## Parameters
* **STRING** szFilename

## Returns
* **INT**

## Notes
<!-- AUTOGENERATED: Remove this line before editing -->
Deletes a cloud file (szFilename) from the member namespace.
This returns an INT that can be used to track this request.
